title: Iowa Caucus Results, SOTU, Rep. French Hill
itunes:title: Iowa Caucus Results, SOTU, Rep. French Hill
description:
Panel Guests: Adam Green, Co-Founder of the Progressive Change Campaign Committee and Jon Seaton, Partner at Camelback Strategy and former National Field Director and Iowa Caucus Director for the John McCain presidential campaign.


Congressman French Hill, a Republican representing Arkansas’s 2nd District previewed President Trump’s State of the Union Speech.
